Voice Recorder Pro 10 brings the following features and improvements: Newly designed professional audio editor the independent waveform editing interface is easier to operate Including many professional functions such as multi regional audio trimming tone and speed accommodation audio split insert and mixing Multiple regions can be set to loop simultaneously Optimized tag function revising and editing are more convenient Performance and stability improvements

Voice Recorder Pro 10.0 brings the following features and improvements: Newly designed professional audio editor the independent waveform editing interface is easier to operate. Including many professional functions such as multi regional audio trimming tone and speed accommodation audio split insert and mixing. Multiple regions can be set to loop simultaneously. Optimized tag function revising and editing are more convenient. Performance and stability improvements
